Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠！你最近去哪了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl! Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}...找橄榄石啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Looking for Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也就几这几天\N{\fnArial\fs48}For a few days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，我知道我也许...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, I know I might have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让你们，失望了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Disappointed all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道石榴还在生我的气，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know Garnet's very upset with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我要向她证明她可以再次信任我\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I'm going to prove to her that she can trust me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:23.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，石榴！我刚刚在寻找橄榄石哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Garnet! I was just looking for Peridot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她肯定在什么地方，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's bound to be somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:26.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有什么新想法吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Any new ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:37.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁想参加公路自驾游？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who wants to go on a road trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...我来的不是时候？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um...Is this a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，请继续\N{\fnArial\fs48}No. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，我要开车去隔壁州-拱顶石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, I gotta drive over to the next state, keystone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:46.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你指，拱顶石州？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You mean, the keystone state?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错，那个州就叫“拱顶石”\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right, the state named keystone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.48,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,200)}“拱顶石州”对应现实中的宾夕法尼亚州。\N格雷格手中册子上的轮廓与宾夕法尼亚州相近，\N且宾夕法尼亚处于最初的13个殖民地中央，曾被称为“The Keystone State”。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我在网上的留言板认识了一个人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I met a guy on an Internet message board
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:53.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}卖的洗车用的刷子简直白菜价！\N{\fnArial\fs48}who's selling car-wash brushes for real cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:55.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只需要到拱顶石州跟他碰头并拿货就好\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just gotta meet him in keystone and pick 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不喜欢那种刷子，用来洗毛发时总感觉怪怪的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't like those brushes. They feel weird on your fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.16,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,70)}详见第一季第6集 Cat Fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，你喜欢汽车旅馆吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, do you like motels? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很可能哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:04.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你愿意在汽车旅馆里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Think you'd like to stay at a motel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}陪你最喜欢的老爸吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}with your favorite dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不觉得你是我的最爱哦...\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know if you're my favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:12.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，你个崽子，给我过来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, you kidder. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:14.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我等不及享受客房服务了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't wait to get room service!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你想的是“饭店”\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're thinking of a {\i1}hotel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:18.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们要去的是“汽车旅馆”\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're going to a {\i1}motel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那里有泳池和免费冰块\N{\fnArial\fs48}It'll have a pool and free ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:25.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且它就在全世界最好的餐厅旁边！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And it's right next to the best diner in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也要去\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm coming, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}更好了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，石榴，我知道我有点过度渲染了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Garnet, I know I'm talking this place up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其实没听上去那么好\N{\fnArial\fs48}but it ain't exactly the ritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.38,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,75)}“the ritz”可能指的是伦敦的五星级酒店The Ritz hotel(利兹酒店)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我自己会做判断的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll be the judge of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，这样的话...公路旅行！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, in that case... Road trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}公路旅行！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Road trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}公路旅行\N{\fnArial\fs48}Road trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好极了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会确保紫晶知道要...\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll make sure Amethyst knows that... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么...再见\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这会很有趣，对吧，老爸？\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is gonna be fun, right, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:02.30,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,200)}现实中也有一家“Keystone Motel”，坐落于St. Pete Beach, Florida。\N那家汽车旅馆曾被宇宙小子的粉丝们恶搞过——有人在Google Plus上\N留下差评，称"马桶被冻住了""披萨是方形的""游泳池被完全蒸发"之类的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}另一个汽车旅馆的优势-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Another great thing about motels --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能直接开到客房门前！\N{\fnArial\fs48}you can drive right up to your door!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我要在泳池里畅游，点播一部大片，享受免费冰块！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm gonna swim in the pool, order a movie, get free ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这次一定会超赞的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's gonna be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}之前先让我检查一下有没有床虱啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not before we check for bedbugs, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好消息！没有床虱！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good news! We're bugless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，有消息了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oop, that's my cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，你不介意在我回来前“守住城堡”吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, do you mind holding down the fort till I get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好，那我去和卖隧道刷的人碰面了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Great. I'm off to see a man about a tunnel brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.04,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,140)}格雷格此处的话是“see a man about a dog/horse”的变种。\N原话从对比赛下注的委婉表达，演变成为避免流露真实原因，用来结束对话的用语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一个网友\N{\fnArial\fs48}An Internet man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果一小时内我没回来，记得报警\N{\fnArial\fs48}If I'm not back in an hour, call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.20,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,140)}格雷格此处的话是“If I'm not back [soon], call the police”的变种\N这里应该是致敬默片时代的Keystone Kops
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好～的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh-kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}跟我一起蹦吧，石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bounce with me, Garnet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或-或者我们也可以看看宣传册子\N{\fnArial\fs48}O-or we could look at brochures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢～拱顶石洞穴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ooh, keystone caverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.46,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,140)}“Keystone Caverns”可能指的是“Crystal Cave”。\N“Crystal Cave”是宾夕法尼亚州东南部的一处自然景观。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HE79069&}要冷静\N{\fnArial\fs48}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H5E37D3&}我不想原谅珍珠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't feel like forgiving Pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HE79069&}我不理解\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HE79069&}我们必须要！\N{\fnArial\fs48}we must!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H5E37D3&}如果你不想听，你可以离开啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}If you're not going to listen, then you can just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们必须放下这件事，红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs48}We must move past this, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她向我们撒谎，好让我们组成红玛瑙！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She lied to us so we'd form sardonyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她骗了我们！你不觉得被利用了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}She tricked us! Don't you feel used?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}红宝石！蓝宝石！我-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ruby! Sapphire! I --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你选择将这件事过度抬高\N{\fnArial\fs48}you're choosing to take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是融合，蓝宝石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's fusion, Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有什么对于我们，相比融合，更重要？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's more personal to us than fusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道你仍然很生气\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know you're still upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，所以只是我喽？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, so it's just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然不是\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你难道看不出我完全被愤怒吞没了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can't you see I'm completely engulfed with rage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，我怎么感觉不到 ？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, it doesn't feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们越早原谅珍珠，\N{\fnArial\fs48}The sooner we forgive Pearl,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对我们所有人都越好\N{\fnArial\fs48}the better it will be for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:35.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你，并非，层次更高，像，你，自以为，那样！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're not as above this as you think you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错，我就是\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不可能永远生她的气\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't stay angry with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:46.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}想赌赌吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wanna bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}红宝石，注意地毯、\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ruby, the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-我都不能-啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You -- I can't even -- ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很高兴，再次见到你？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nice to see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很高兴见到你\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nice to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你想在泳池里游泳吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You wanna swim in the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这可是融合，史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's fusion, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}感觉蓝宝石根本就不在乎！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's like Sapphire doesn't even care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}“而且我们应该用'成年人'的视角看问题”\N{\fnArial\fs48}And we're supposed to be the bigger gem about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们，一，直，是，"成年人"！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're {\i1}always{\i} {\i1}the bigger gem!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，不行！这次不行！这件事！不行！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, not this time! Not about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来吧，为什么不在泳池里先冷静一下呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, why don't you come cool down in the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我，才不需要冷-静呢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't need to cool down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快啊，红宝石，水很爽～哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, Ruby. The water's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么她，总是，表现的像，我才是，荒谬的一方？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why does she always act like I'm being ridiculous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就只因为她想伪装成\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just because she wants to pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}自己没有感情一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}that she doesn't have feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}红宝石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你把泳池变成温泉了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You made a warm spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！是“烫泉”了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah! A hot spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}水开了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Boiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，我还是回屋吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, I'm gonna go back to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蓝宝石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sapphire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:54.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你好，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hello, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你...还-还-还好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}A-are you... D-d-doin' okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-很-好\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好-吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}想-想一起看电视吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}W-wanna watch TV together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:04.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可以\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈，频道的号码都乱了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh. The channels are all the wrong numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿～你能用你的预知能力\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, can you use your future powers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}预测一下我最喜欢的频道吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}to predict what channel I'd love the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯...43，但也没什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm...43. But there's not much on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.42,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,160)}宾夕法尼亚州的43频道为标清Nickelodeon(尼克)台。Nickelodeon为\NCartoon Network(卡通网络，”宇宙小子“的东家)的竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，蓝宝石...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Sapphire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}即使我这样做，红宝石也不会听的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Even if I do, Ruby won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你会说我该和红宝石谈谈\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're going to say I should talk to Ruby,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这没用\N{\fnArial\fs48}but it won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但-但她看起来非常生气\N{\fnArial\fs48}B-but she seems really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这无关紧要\N{\fnArial\fs48}That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她不可能永远生珍珠的气，\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can't stay mad at Pearl forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且她也不可能永远生我的气，\N{\fnArial\fs48}and she can't stay mad at me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且之后她会回心转意并发现我是对的\N{\fnArial\fs48}And then she'll come back and see that I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你-你确-确-确定？\N{\fnArial\fs48}A-a-are you s-sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我能看到命运的轨迹一路延伸到时间的地平线\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can see the path of fate as it stretches toward the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}红宝石躲避不了宿命\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ruby can't avoid the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她只是在让自己的情绪失控\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's just letting her emotions get out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}N-n-not you, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:55.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我...得去卫生间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm...Going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}同样无法避免\N{\fnArial\fs48}Also inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蓝宝石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sapphire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}马桶冻住了\N{\fnArial\fs48}The toilet's frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是命啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Such is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那我也注定要去外面的草地上尿了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Am I fated to pee outside on the grass, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}拱顶石州...\N{\fnArial\fs48}"Keystone state"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，小子，我带晚餐了哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, stu-ball, I brought dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，老爸，怎么样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, dad. How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，他以前不是个凶手，这还不错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, he wasn't an ex-murderer, so that was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你穿着浴衣在外面干什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you doing outside in your bathing suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且石榴在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}And where's Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他不会喜欢方形\N{\fnArial\fs48}He's not going to like that it's square.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，天哪，另一个呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, boy. Where's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在原来是泳池的地方散步呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's pacing around in what used to be the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有些非常严重的事情发生了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Something pretty serious must be going on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果都能让石榴分裂了的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}if it made Garnet split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，嘿，我们仍能高兴起来啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}But hey, we can still have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}方形的披萨？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Square Pizza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.38,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}第二季第2集说好的不介意任何基本形状呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个疯狂的州怎么了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's wrong with this crazy state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.66,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,194)}“方形披萨”可能指的是宾夕法尼亚州东北部非常流行的“Old Forge style pizza”。\N“Old Forge style pizza”通常使用American cheese，\N而且通常叫"tray"(盘)和"cut"(块)，而非"pie"(张)和"slice"(片)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}儿子，你生命中总有些时候\N{\fnArial\fs48}Son, there'll come a time in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}得学会接受所有的披萨\N{\fnArial\fs48}when you learn to accept all Pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么红宝石和蓝宝石直接，和好呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why can't Ruby and Sapphire just make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有的时候相互爱恋的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sometimes people that love each other
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可能会无意中相互伤害\N{\fnArial\fs48}can hurt each other's feelings without meaning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们应该给他们点空间\N{\fnArial\fs48}We should just give them some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:05.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我觉得她们能解决这个问题\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I think they'd work it out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果她们愿意沟通的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}if they'd just talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}明天早上一切都会变好的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everything will be better in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们都要去世界上最好的餐厅\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'll all go to the best diner in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们将吃到世界上最好的早餐\N{\fnArial\fs48}where they'll eat the best breakfast in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你觉得这有用吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You think that'll help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没什么能像早餐一样让人们团聚\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nothing like a little breakfast to bring people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你确实是我最喜欢的老爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}You really are my favorite dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我就知道这份披萨能帮到我\N{\fnArial\fs48}I knew this Pizza would put me over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:27.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.80,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,152)}“世界上最好的餐厅”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么了？不饿吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's the matter? Not hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}宝石人不用吃饭，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gems don't need to eat, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，石榴有时会吃啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Eh, Garnet likes to eat sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！显然，石榴，不，在！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh! Well, Garnet's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}唔，我的天！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mmm. Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这-真的是-世界上-最好的餐厅！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This really is the best diner in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在晃桌子\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're shaking the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢？！哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh?! Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我，很好奇你居然还，有点感情，说实话！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm kinda surprised you felt anything at all, to be honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-不需要-感觉，我能看到\N{\fnArial\fs48}I didn't {\i1}need{\i} to feel -- I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:10.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所，有，事你都，看，得，一清，二楚，不，是，吗？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everything's just so crystal clear to you, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:12.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这会过去了\N{\fnArial\fs48}This will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她迟早会让自己熄火的\N{\fnArial\fs48}She'll eventually just burn herself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是你，的，想，法！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是永不熄灭的烈焰，baby！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I am an eternal flame, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.14,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&H5E37D3&}你又不了解我！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.06,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HE79069&\pos(960,240)}我怎么可能不了解\N{\fnArial\fs48}How could I possibly not know you 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.88,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&H5E37D3&}你看看你！嗷～嚎-嚎\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look at you! Awww-haw-haw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.28,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HE79069&\pos(960,240)}我们总是融合在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}we always fused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.70,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&H5E37D3&}你都不了解你自己！哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't even know yourself! Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，这没什么，伙计！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, it's okay, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.30,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HE79069&\pos(960,240)}看看你自己，看看你在干什么...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look at you. Look at what you're going on about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们仍然能解决的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can still save this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们为什么不讲这些打包带走然后-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why don't we just bag these up to go and --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，天哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}ah, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当石榴说她要和我与爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was so happy when Garnet said
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一起旅行时我还很高兴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}she was gonna come on this trip with me and dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}家里糟透了，这里也糟透了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Home's been awful. Here's been awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以为你们想放松一下\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought you wanted to have a fun time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但每个人也都表现的非常糟糕！\N{\fnArial\fs48}but everyone's been acting awful, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这种氛围-这种氛围一直跟着我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}It -- it just came with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我就不理解了，是-这是因为我吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't understand. Is it -- is it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No!Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，都是我们的错！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, it's all us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我们让他感觉这都是他的错\N{\fnArial\fs48}But we made him feel like it was his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:03.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我总是关注着未来\N{\fnArial\fs48}I keep looking into the future
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那时这一切都已经被解决了\N{\fnArial\fs48}when all of this has already been solved,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就好像你当下的感受毫无意义一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}as if it doesn't matter how you feel in the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:13.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}难怪-你觉得-我毫不-在乎！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No wonder you think I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:14.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蓝宝石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不不不不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这都是我的错！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我并不想寻找解决方法\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I didn't want to look for a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是在犯孩子气而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just wanted to be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是对的，你一直是对的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're right. You're always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我之前犯傻了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不觉得你笨！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't think you're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我，对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm,sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你真的认为我对已经发生的毫不在意？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You honestly think I'm not upset about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:37.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-只是试着做正确的事而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was just trying to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道分开的好处是什么吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know what's nice about being split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:44.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我能看到你了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I get to look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:47.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噗！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pfft! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}严肃点！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这才是我的爱笑的小蓝嘛！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's my laffy saffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘘！你这是在史蒂文面前放闪光弹啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Shh! You're embarrassing me in front of Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，我为早餐付过钱了...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, I paid for breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有桌子损坏的费用\N{\fnArial\fs48}And the damage to the booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不管怎么说，我觉得我放够假了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Anyhoo, I think I'm all vacationed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}准备好收拾东西了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ready to call it a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}先得拿到免费冰块再说！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not before we get our free ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们到家～啦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.68,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HB4C7E6&\pos(960,120)}我不知道为什么我总是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just don't know why I keep--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！呃-你们看起来过得很开心啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!Ah-you look like you all had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是啊，问题解决了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, it all worked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，你感觉怎么样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是现在\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她总算又和我说话了...算是\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's speaking to me again...Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那真是一次超棒的旅行\N{\fnArial\fs48}That really was a great trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们能再去一次吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许吧...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe one day... But not to that diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但-不算那家餐馆\N{\fnArial\fs48}But not to that diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:47.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，天哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, boy.
